While use new project, It requires selenium, robotframework, robotframework-seleniumlibrary.
pycharm->settings->project->choose the project->project interpreter->search those 3 libraries and click on "Install Packages".
extension of testcase -> .robot
Browser drivers need to be installed prior.

There are sections while writing Testcase - Settings, Variables, Test Cases, Keywords.
In keyword section, own keyword can be created.
These sections can be used in same file or the different file.
Sections are mandatory. content is non mandatory.
Here instead space, tab has to given.

Robot framework can run only via terminal.
Ex: robot directoryname/filenamewithextension

Robot Framework keyword reference-> https://robotframework.org/SeleniumLibrary/SeleniumLibrary.html
